column85: Level II requires a detailed understanding and application of financial theories, formulas, etc. to security analysis. It is imperative that you understand the why and I believe its best to think about difficult topics via the bigger picture. Having said that, Level II was incredibly interesting and ties together topics that were brushed on in Level I. It also helps with real world investing and understanding market intricacies.
